awton, Devon, England":"норт тавтон, девон, Англия","lifeSummary":"Когда John de Valletort родился в 1240 г. в местности норт тавтон, девон, Англия, его отцу по имени Philip de Valletort было 31 год, а матери, которую звали Joan de Cornwall, 28. Он женился на женщине по имени Mary de Columbiéres в 1260 г. в местности модбури, девон, Англия, Великобритания. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын. Он умер в 1294 г. в его родном городе в возрасте 54 лет и был похоронен в местности модбури, девон, Англия."},"sm":{"1240–1294":"1240–1294","1245–1290":"1245–1290","1270–1310":"1270–1310","1210–1259":"1210–1259","1212–1300":"1212–1300","about 1270":"e tusa o le 1270","Abt 1259":"e tusa o le 1259","1240":"1240","1294":"1294","1260":"1260","1270":"1270","1290":"1290","Bef 1240":"a'e le'I oo le 1240","1259":"1259","1300":"1300","1212":"1212","1245":"1245","1310":"1310","1210":"1210","Stowey, Somerset, England":"Stowey, Somerset, Egelani","Modbury, Devonshire, England":"Modbury, Devon, Egelani, United Kingdom","England":"Egelani","Modbury, Devon, England":"Modbury, Devon, Egelani, United Kingdom","Tawton, Devon, England":"Devon, Egelani, United Kingdom","North Tawton, Devon, England":"North Tawton, Devon, Egelani"},"sk":{"1240–1294":"1240–1294","1245–1290":"1245–1290","1270–1310":"1270–1310","1210–1259":"1210–1259","1212–1300":"1212–1300","about 1270":"okolo 1270","Abt 1259":"okolo 1259","1240":"1240","1294":"1294","1260":"1260","1270":"1270","1290":"1290","Bef 1240":"pred rokom 1240","1259":"1259","1300":"1300","1212":"1212","1245":"1245","1310":"1310","1210":"1210","Stowey, Somerset, England":"Stowey, Somerset, England","Modbury, Devonshire, England":"Modbury, Devon, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","England":"England","Modbury, Devon, England":"Modbury, Devon, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Tawton, Devon, England":"Devon, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","North Tawton, Devon, England":"North Tawton, Devon, England"},"es":{"1240–1294":"1240–1294","1245–1290":"1245–1290","1270–1310":"1270–1